  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Taijutsu </p><p>You have practiced extensively with a variety of weapons, gaining the following benefits: </p><p>• Increase your Strength or Dexterity score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</p><p>• You gain proficiency with four weapons of your choice.</p><p>• Select one weapon, with which you are proficient.</p><p> Once per turn, when you roll damage for the chosen weapon, you can reroll its damage, using either total.</p><p>• Once per turn, when you would cast a Bukijutsu using a weapon, your weapon increases its weapon damage die by +1.</p><p></p>",
